  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK996">
<l>paṇpuṭaiyārp paṭṭuṇ ṭulaka matuviṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>maṇpukku māyvatu maṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The (way of the) world subsists by contact with the good; if not, it would bury itself in the earth and perish.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
